sequenceDiagram
  participant G as Glasses
  participant B as Bridge
  participant H as Hermes agent
  G->>B: hello {token}
  B-->>G: hello.ok
  G->>B: text
  B->>H: handle_message
  H-->>B: streamed reply (full accumulated)
  B-->>G: assistant.delta (diffed, cursor stripped)
  H-->>B: pre / post tool_call
  B-->>G: tool.start / tool.end
  B-->>G: turn.done (when idle)
